 \frac{\ddot{a}}{a} & = & -\frac{4\pi G}{3F}\left[\rho_{\rm m}+2\dot{\Phi}^2-2U\right.\nonumber\\
                    & &   +\left.3M_{\rm pl}^2(\ddot{F}+H\dot{F})\right]\;.\label{eqn:addot}
\end{eqnarray}
Note that equation~(\ref{eqn:addot}) corrects a typo in equation~22 of \cite{Pace2014}.

